zebra.name: zebra
zebra.contactinfo: GNU Network Object Model Environment project see http://www.gnome.org for contact persons of a particular area or subproject of GNOME. Administrative contact for MIB module: Jochen Friedrich Wingertstr. 70/1 68809 Neulussheim Germany email: snmp@gnome.org
zebra.description: The product registrations for the various zebra subdeamons. These registrations are guaranteed to be unique and are used for SMUX registration by default (if not overridden manually).

zserv.name: zserv
zserv.description: zserv is part of the zebra project which again is a GNU endorsed internet routing program. zserv is the main zebra process which implements routing entries with the kernel and handles routing updates between other routing protocols.
